#     ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą    ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėí     
#       ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí      ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí  ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí ‚Ėí‚Ėí‚Ėí       

# function d_c(p: player, i: integer): 
#     loop circle({_p}, 1, 100, vector(0,1,0), {_i}):
#         set {_n} to (vector from {_p} to loop-location)
#         set vector length of {_n} to 0.2
#         draw 0 end rod particles with an offset ({_n} + vector(0,1,0)) at loop-location # middle({_p})
#         wait 1 tick

function animate_roll(p: player, seff: text):
    set {_u} to uuid of {_p}
    set {_ticks} to 0
    set {_rot} to 0

    play sound "block.respawn_anchor.charge" with pitch 0.5 at {_p}
    play sound "block.beacon.activate" with pitch 2 at {_p}
    loop {_eff} in {infuse::effects::*}:
        if {_eff} is not "earth" or "ender":
            spawn text display at (location 1 block below {_p})
            set {_e} to last spawned text display
            set {_se} to last spawned text display if {_eff} is {_seff}

            set billboard of {_e} to center
            set the teleport duration of {_e} to 1 ticks
            add nbt from "{background:0}" to nbt of {_e}
            set text of {_e} to {-infuse::icon::%{_eff}%::default-normal::1}
            add {_e} to {_disp::*}
    
    # loop 0, 60, 120, 180, 240 and 300:
    #     d_c({_p}, loop-value)

    while {_ticks} < 100:
        if {_p} is not online:
            kill {_disp::*}
            stop
        add 3 to {_rot}
        if {_rot} > 360:
            remove 360 from {_rot}
        set {_origin} to eye location of {_p}
        set {_count} to size of {_disp::*}
        if {_count} is 0:
            stop
        loop {_e} in {_disp::*}:
            set {_i} to loop-iteration-2
            if {_e} is alive:
                set {_v} to vector(1.8, -0.7, 0)
                rotate {_v} around y-axis by {_rot} + ({_i} * (360 / {_count}))
                set {_target} to {_origin} ~ {_v}
                add (0.15 * sin({_rot} * 2 + ({_i} * 90))) to y-coord of {_target}
                teleport {_e} to {_target}
            else:
                remove {_e} from {_disp::*}

        wait 1 tick
        add 1 to {_ticks}

    teleport {_disp::*} to middle({_p})
    wait 2 ticks
    kill {_disp::*} except {_se}
    clear {_disp::*}
    
    loop flat_circle(middle({_p}), 1, {_i}, 80):
        set {_n} to (vector from middle({_p}) to loop-location)
        set vector length of {_n} to 0.6
        draw (0 end rod particles with an offset {_n}) at middle({_p})
    play sound "block.beacon.power_select" with pitch 0.9 at {_p}

    set {_icon} to {-infuse::icon::%{_seff}%::default-normal::1}
    set {_display_name} to join ((the first character of {_seff}) in uppercase) and subtext of {_seff} from characters 2 to (the length of {_seff})
    
    send title ("%{_icon}%") with subtitle ("&e%{_display_name}% Effect") to {_p} for (2 seconds) with fadein (10 ticks) and fadeout (10 ticks)
    
    teleport {_se} to location 0.5 block above eye of {_p}
    wait 40 tick
    teleport {_se} to location 1 block below {_p}
    wait 2 tick
    kill {_se}

command /roll <text>:
    trigger:
        animate_roll(player, arg-1)

